VIEQUES. POST NOTES THAT THE VISIT OF THE PUERTO RICAN 
DELEGATION AND ITS ARRANGEMENTS WITH THE VATICAN ITSELF 
OCCURRED WITHOUT REFERENCE TO THIS EMBASSY. POLOFF, 
ATTENDING THE BEATIFICATION - A VATICAN \"STATE EVENT\" - 
NOTED A SEA OF PUERTO RICAN FLAGS WAVED BY THE MORE THAN 
 
