IN SOUTH KOREA, KATHI ZELLWEGER OF CARITAS HONG KONG (REFTEL 
C) SAID NORTH KOREA IS THREATENED BY A SEVERE FAMINE. 
ACCORDING TO ZELLWEGER, ONLY 5 PERCENT OF AN EXPECTED US 
 
