--------------------------------------------- ------ 
 
5.   THE VATICAN\'S REPRESENTATIVE TO THE U.N. EDUCATIONAL, 
SCIENTIFIC AND CULTURAL ORGANIZATION, MONSIGNOR LORENZO FRANA, 
HAS SAID THE ORGANIZATION\'S ROLE IS THE SAME AS IT WAS IN THE 
YEARS AFTER THE SECOND WORLD WAR - \"TO RAISE HUMAN SPIRITS TO 
THE DEFENSE OF PEACE, A STABLE PEACE BUILT ON THE FOUNDATION 
 
