SUBJECT: VENEZUELAN AMBASSADOR TO RETURN TO CARACAS 
AS FOREIQN MINISTER 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
PAGE 02        VATICA  00025  021624Z 
 
CLASSIFIED BY CHARQE JOSEPH MERANTE, REASON E.O. 
12958 1.5 (B,D) 
 
1.  (C)  IQNACIO QUINTANA, THE VENEZUELAN AMBASSADOR 
TO THE HOLY SEE, HOSTED A DINER IN HONOR OF VATICAN 
PRIME MINISTER-EQUIVALENT CARDINAL SODANO ON 
DECEMBER 27.  IN ADDITION TO AMBASSADOR NICHOLSON, 
THE TWELVE QUESTS INCLUDED FOREIQN MINISTER- 
EQUIVALENT ARCHBISHOP TAURAN, AND PREFECT OF THE 
PAPAL HOUSEHOLD ARCHBISHOP JAMES HARVEY.  DURINQ THE 
COURSE OF THE LAVISH DINNER, WHICH WAS HELD IN A 
PRIVATE ROOM AT THE ST. REQIS GRAND, CONVERSATION 
TURNED TO THE QUINTANA\'S ALREADY ANNOUNCED FEBRUARY 
DEPARTURE.  THERE WAS OPEN DISCUSSION ON QUINTANA\'S 
RETURN TO CARACAS TO ASSUME THE POST OF FOREIQN 
MINISTER. 
 
2.  (C) AT PAPAL CEREMONY ON JANUARY 1, QUINTANA 
APPROACHED AMBASSADOR AND TOLD HIM THAT RELATIONS 
BETWEEN THE U.S. AND VENEZUELA WILL SOON BECOME MUCH 
WARMER. 
 
3.  (C)  COMMENT:  DURINQ HIS YEAR AS AMBASSADOR, 
QUINTANA HAS BEEN AN ENIQMA.  WITHIN THE EXTREMELY 
RESERVED, CULTURED AMBASSADORIAL CORPS, HE WAS A 
BACKSLAPPINQ, QREQARIOUS EXCEPTION.  VATICAN 
OFFICIALS OFTEN SPOKE DESPAIRINQLY OF HIM, AS WELL 
AS THE POLICIES OF VENEZUELA.  HOWEVER, THE FACT 
THAT SODANO, TAURAN, AND HARVEY ALL ATTENDED A 
DINNER HOSTED BY HIM, DURINQ A PERIOD IN WHICH 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        VATICA  00025  021624Z 
SOCIAL EVENTS ARE BASICALLY SUSPENDED FOR THE 
HOLIDAYS, IS A STRONG INDICATION THAT THEY BELIEVE 
QUINTANA IS SOMEONE THEY WILL NEED IN THE FUTURE. 
 
4.  (C) COMMENT CONT:  QUINTANA HAS ALSO TAKEN A 
VERY UNUSUAL STAND IN HIS RELATIONSHIP WITH 
AMBASSADOR NICHOLSON AND THE U.S. EMBASSY.  DURINQ 
ALMOST EVERY ENCOUNTER WITH AMBASSADOR, QUINTANA 
MAKES AN ALMOST THEATRICAL PRESENTATION ON HOW MUCH 
HE \"LOVES\" THE UNITED STATES. 
MERANTE 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
