--  POLOFF ESCORTED 03/25 OSCE HOM ROBERT BEECROFT TO 
COURTESY CALL WITH AMBASSADOR AND THEN TO MEETING WITH 
VATICAN FM TAURAN.  BEECROFT DETAILED TO TAURAN HIS 
