CHAIR HELGA KONRAD.  SPANISH AMBASSADOR TO HOLY SEE HELPED 
LOCK-IN PARTICIPATION BY PONTIFICAL COUNCILS FOR JUSTICE AND 
PEACE AND MIGRANTS.  VARIOUS OTHER EMBASSIES ACCREDITED TO 
HOLY SEE FORWARDED SPEAKER SUGGESTIONS. 
 
9. (C)  REPORTING: VATICAN 1152: SANT\'EGIDIO THANKS UNCLE SAM 
AND CHIDES \"HYPOCRITE\" FIDEL; VATICAN 1171: VATICAN\'S \"OTHER\" 
INTERESTS IN THE MIDDLE EAST; VATICAN 1176: ANDORRA TO OPEN 
