REMINDED HIM OF THE STATE DEPARTMENT OFFICE OF INTERNATIONAL 
RELIGIOUS FREEDOM, NOTING THAT WE HAD A REGULAR CHANNEL WITH 
THE VATICAN ON RELIGIOUS FREEDOM ISSUES.  SAYING \"THANK GOD 
FOR AMERICA -- THE ONLY COUNTRY THAT WILL STAND UP AND TALK 
ABOUT THESE ISSUES,\" TRICARICO INDICATED HE WOULD WELCOME AN 
OPPORTUNITY TO SHARE VIEWS WITH THE NEW AMBASSADOR AT LARGE 
OR INTERNATIONAL RELIGIOUS FREEDOM IF AND WHEN HE VISITS 
VATICAN CITY. 
 
6. (C) COMMENT: POST HAS OBSERVED ARCHBISHOP TRICARICO TO BE 
MORE EMOTIONAL IN HIS DISCOURSE THAN ARE MOST OTHER VATICAN 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 02        VATICA  02239  02 OF 02  081447Z 
COUNTRY DIRECTORS.   PERHAPS BECAUSE OF HIS AGE (HE WILL TURN 
75 LATER THIS YEAR AND SUBMIT HIS RESIGNATION) HIS VIEWS ON 
THE ORTHODOX CLERGY\'S \"COLLABORATIONIST\" PROCLIVITIES ARE 
SHARPENED.  PRIOR TO TAKING MFA RESPONSIBILITIES FOR RUSSIA 
AND THE NIS COUNTRIES, TRICARICO HAD BEEN NUNCIO IN S/E ASIA 
FOR MYANMAR AND LAOS, AND HAD SERVED IN VARIOUS EUROPEAN 
NUNCIATURES.  WHILE TIRCARICO SOUNDED TO US SOMEWHAT 
CONFRONTATIONAL ON THE RUSSIAN ISSUES, WE BELIEVE THAT THE 
VATICAN ITSELF WILL, TRUE TO FORM, TAKE A LONG VIEW OF THE 
PROBLEM AND WORK PATIENTLY AND DISCRETELY TO ADVANCE ITS 
INTERESTS. EMBASSY CONVERSATIONS WITH RUSSIAN EMBASSY AND 
ORTHODOX CHURCH REPRESENTATIVES IN ROME WILL BE REPORTED 
SEPTEL. 
NICKOLSON 
 
