IRRI IN THE PHILIPPINES AND THE CYMMT IN MEXICO, IN A PROJECT 
COORDINATED WITH EMBASSY ROME FAS. (NOTE: WE HAVE ALREADY 
RAISED THIS IDEA AT THE MFA WORKING LEVEL, AND THEY ARE 
ENTHUSIASTIC). 
 
13. (U) THIS CABLE WAS CLEARED WITH FODAG AND EMBASSY ROME. 
NICHOLSON 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
