"3352","7/23/2002 14:56","02VATICAN3633","Embassy Vatican","UNCLASSIFIED//FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY","02VATICAN444","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

","UNCLAS SECTION 01 OF 03 VATICAN 003633 
 
