"3355","7/23/2002 15:01","02VATICAN3637","Embassy Vatican","UNCLASSIFIED//FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY","02VATICAN290","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

","UNCLAS SECTION 01 OF 02 VATICAN 003637 
 
