"3427","8/2/2002 14:09","02VATICAN3823","Embassy Vatican","CONFIDENTIAL","02VATICAN3492|02VATICAN3503|02VATICAN3527|02VATICAN3823","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

