SUBSEQUENTLY WITH THE PAPAL NUNCIO IN ZAMBIA THIS WEEK. 
HE PLEDGED TO GET BACK TO THE AMBASSADOR AFTER THESE 
CONSULTATIONS. 
7. (SBU) THE AMBASSADOR DEFINITELY GOT SANDRI\'S 
ATTENTION.  HE VISIBLY WINCED WHEN HE POINTED OUT THE 
CONTRAST BETWEEN GREENPEACE AND THE HOLY SEE. 
