PRESIDENTIAL ADDRESS TO THE DIPLOMATIC CORPS.  FROM OUR 
PERSPECTIVE, THOSE REMARKS COULD OFFER AN OPPORTUNITY TO 
ENGAGE THE HOLY SEE ALONG THE LINES OF REF A INSTRUCTION. 
EMBASSY VATICAN IS PREPARED TO PRESS HARDER, AND AT A HIGHER 
LEVEL, IF WASHINGTON AND CARACAS BELIEVE HOLY SEE ENGAGEMENT 
IN THE VENEZUELAN CONFLICT WOULD BE USEFUL. 
