OR NO FREEDOM OF MOVEMENT.  ACCORDING TO DURAK, SOME OF THESE 
PEOPLE ARE NEVER ABLE TO EARN THE MONEY NECESSARY TO LEAVE 
SAUDI ARABIA AND RETURN HOME, WHILE OTHERS ARE ACTUALLY HELD 
-- ALMOST PHYSICALLY -- AGAINST THEIR WILL. 
 
