conference in Miami titled: \"Invisible Chains: A Call to 
Action Against Human Slavery.\"  This conference is a direct 
result of our June Trafficking in Persons conference in 
Rome, and is co-hosted by one of the speakers at our 
conference, Michelle Gillen of CBS News (Miami). 
Ambassador John Miller, Director of the Office to Monitor 
and Combat Trafficking In Persons (G/TIP) has also been 
