Ambassador to the Holy See.  The award consists of a framed 
picture of the \"Mother of Humility,\" the patron saint of 
the NAC.  The additional flight leg to Washington is 
included in the Miami flight as it was the same cost as the 
Miami-only ticket.  The NAC has offered to provide two 
nights lodging for the Ambassador and Mrs. Nicholson.  All 
travel / lodging is to be provided in kind. 
 
